==Finnish==

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|ˈkuːsi}}

===Etymology (1)===
From Finno-Ugric ''[[*kutte]]''. Cognates include Estonian [[kuus]] and Hungarian [[hat#Hungarian|hat]].

===Cardinal number===
'''kuusi'''

#[[six]]

